timeline.bodyText:
in reference to Jon's comment here, it's true that it's not really standard for Java samples to contain abstracted methods, such as here, for what is a pretty straightforward initialiser. Adding map image layers to the map's operational layers are a key part of this sample, so it's better to show the ArcGISMapImageLayers instantiated right up front.
We can shorthand it a little with the following:




